sniffexipv6.cpp displays all traffic on the ethernet

sniffexV2.cpp will try to display IPv4 and IPv6 TCP traffic only
Currently, it can display 10 packets of both IPv4 and IPv6 traffic, though 
not necessarily TCP

sniffexV5.cpp is the newest version. It uses a struct for IPv6 from bro source code.

To compile, please do the following command

g++ sniffexV5.cpp -o sniffexV5 -lpcap

or something along those lines


